'''''Poacher''''' ni [[Kenya|film ngufi ya Kenya]] / [[Ubwongereza]] yasohotse  2018 iyobowe na Tom Whitworth<ref>https://www.standardmedia.co.ke/entertainment/arts-and-culture/2001388367/locally-shot-short-film-poacher-to-premier-on-netflix-today</ref>. Iyi filime yitabiriwe n'abantu benshi nyuma yo gusohoka muri Netflix muri Nzeri 2020<ref>https://hagertyjourn.com/14483/editorials/reviews/poacher-brings-a-trunk-load-of-storytelling-to-netflix/</ref>.  Yabaye kandi filime ya mbere yo muri Kenya yasohotse binyuze kuri Netflix<ref>https://www.pd.co.ke/entertainment/actor-brian-ogola-starred-in-a-2018-short-film-poacher-53571/</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Yakozwe mu buryo butangaje bwa firime, ''Poacher'' ivuga amateka y’umuhinzi wihebye uhura n’ibibazo nyuma yo kwiba igiti cy’amahembe y’inzovu mu gatsiko k’iterabwoba <ref>https://khusoko.com/2020/09/03/kenyas-conservation-film-poacher-to-air-on-netflix-sept-30/</ref>. Iyi filime irashaka kwerekana ikibazo gikomeye mpuzamahanga cy’ubucuruzi bw’inzovu mu buryo butemewe hifashishijwe ibibazo by’abaturage, inzovu ziri mu kaga muri [[Afurika]]<ref>http://www.gautengfilm.org.za/news/news-archive/2011/january-2011/775-afda-students-shoots-rhino-poaching-movie-on-film</ref>. 

