== Umusaruro ==
''Poacher'' yafashwe amashusho muminsi itandatu muri parike yigihugu ya Tsavo yuburengerazuba bwamajyepfo yumurwa mukuru wa Kenya, Nairobi<ref>https://www.kenyanvibe.com/kenyan-film-poacher-to-be-aired-on-netflix/</ref>. Umusaruro warimo abanyamuryango n'abakozi barenga 30<ref>https://www.huntleyarchives.com/results.asp?txtkeys1=poacher</ref>.  Umuyobozi Tom Whitworth yasebeje umuyobozi wa mbere ukiri muri filime ku ya 10 Mata 2018, atangaza ko sinema yakozwe na Nathan Prior na Ishmael Azeli. Byagaragaye ko filime ngufi yabanje gutekerezwa nk'ikinamico ya TV<ref>https://www.triplep.tv/article.php?jmk=MjU4</ref>. 

== Kurekura ==
''Poacher (2018)'' yarekuwe muri Kanama 2018, imaze kwerekanwa mu iserukiramuco rigufi kugeza ku ngingo (STTP)<ref>https://www.kenyans.co.ke/news/57023-award-winning-kenyan-film-make-history-netflix</ref>, atoranyirizwa igihembo cya ''Best Editing'' Award ''.''  Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere muri Kenya mu nzu mberabyombi ya ANGA IMAX ku ya 10 Ugushyingo 2018 muri ''Kalasha International Film Awards'' i [[Nairobi]] <ref>https://theafrikantales.wordpress.com/2020/09/29/poacher-movie-review/</ref>.  ''Poacher'' yanerekanywe mu ''iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema mpuzamahanga rya'' Moscou 2018 muri Nzeri 2018 i Moscou.  Iyi filime yanyujijwe kuri Netflix ku ya 30 Nzeri 2020<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/film/fichefilm_gen_cfilm=249836.html</ref>.

